        "### Setting Up your IDL environment",
        "",
        "You can develop IDL code in multiple ways, notably:",
        "",
        "- **IDL Development Environment (the IDL Workbench)**  ",
        "  Our dedicated Development Environment for building and debugging IDL applications.",
        "",
        "- **IDL for VS Code Extension**  ",
